|2 |  └─SORT                   |             |4       |890         |
|3 |    └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN     |             |4       |889         |
|4 |      ├─HASH JOIN          |             |3       |841         |
|5 |      │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |date_dim     |2       |22          |
|6 |      │ └─HASH JOIN        |             |3       |819         |
|7 |      │   ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|item         |3       |14          |
|8 |      │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN|inventory    |3053    |548         |
|9 |      └─TABLE RANGE SCAN   |catalog_sales|2       |16          |
====================================================================
